Logical Model: 照顧管理評估量表邏輯模型

Official URL: http://ltc-ig.fhir.tw/StructureDefinition/LTCCMSModel Version: 0.3.0
Active as of 2025-09-26 Computable Name: LTCCMSModel

此邏輯模型以衛生福利部長期照顧管理中心照顧管理評估量表為基礎，用以描述照顧管理評估量表的資料結構與欄位準備指引。

Usages:

  • This Logical Model is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.
